  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939420/extras/c0ccb173cb8a01681e1fe192b2589141.avif?t=1744358451\" width=617 height=194 /></span><br>In Battimals players will use the DNA of an array of animals to build up a team of four unique battle animals, known as Battimals. These Battimal will compete head to head against other players’ Battimals in online matches, where only one team can be victorious.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939420/extras/d6772e626f73171d1eee73d4c44b797a.poster.avif?t=1744358451\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939420/extras/d6772e626f73171d1eee73d4c44b797a.webm?t=1744358451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939420/extras/f9803528be17a884183f693dd96cc117.avif?t=1744358451\" width=617 height=194 /></span><br>Through the blending of each new animal’s DNA, the player’s Battimals will transform, taking on a percentage of the appearance of each animal added, as well as that particular animal’s stats.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939420/extras/6f09da312d0ea3050f83e7c77940e8a0.avif?t=1744358451\" width=617 height=374 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939420/extras/fe0c149a72471a50d58e7d577d9e08c6.avif?t=1744358451\" width=617 height=195 /></span><br>Compete in 8-player online matches consisting of multiple rounds. Match up with opponents through online matchmaking, or create your own lobby and invite your friends.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939420/extras/4b871acd11cdb23c4edc4eb8f3c09288.avif?t=1744358451\" width=617 height=374 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939420/extras/7449ff8bd16345c68450649224a17d65.avif?t=1744358451\" width=617 height=194 /></span><br>Rely not only on the Battimals blended stats to get the edge but also on a multitude of available upgrades that boost those stats. As well as choosing the strategic battle positioning for each Battimal allowing for a more defensive or evasive play.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939420/extras/f92ecc582f4dddc37fb1dc217eaf4c4f.avif?t=1744358451\" width=617 height=173 /></span><br>With over 50 animals to choose from players have over a quadrillion different combinations of Battimals to create and compete with, guaranteeing that nearly every match will have a new Battimal that hasn’t been seen before.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2939420/extras/1867ea18c37474b581bfe48401b39444.avif?t=1744358451\" width=617 height=605 /></span>",
